STEP1: 
FFmpeg Installation (Required)
This project requires FFmpeg for audio processing.
Windows
Download FFmpeg from:
https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/
C:\ffmpeg\bin\ffmpeg.exe
C:\ffmpeg\bin\ffprobe.exe

